In cyber security, encryption is the essential process (such as ) to ensure that the data is only accessible by those with the right credentials. Imagine that you can collect sufficient number of data in the form of (clear text, encrypted text).

Whether it is possible for data science platform with the right data analytics (or machine learning) algorithms to reveal the function that can maps the encrypted text to the clear text? [1 mark]
If yes, please state why and how? If not, please state why and under which situation it will be possible.
[2 marks]
(Note: If you are familiar with encryption, you can divide the cases as “with a secret key” and “without a
secret key”.)
